data.description: Introducing your dream home in South Boise! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath two-story house is a gem waiting for your family to make it their own. Nestled among the charm of mature trees, this property has a 2-car garage, perfect for your vehicles and storage needs. You'll love the convenience of RV parking, providing plenty of space for your adventurous spirit. Enjoy the benefits of a storage shed attached to the house for all your gardening and outdoor equipment, as well as an additional detached storage shed for even more storage solutions. With a thoughtful design, this home offers a comfortable and versatile layout. The four bedrooms provide ample space for family and guests, while the 2.5 bathrooms ensure morning routines run smoothly. The two stories offer separation and privacy when needed. This property is more than just a house; it's a place to create lasting memories and enjoy the South Boise lifestyle. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
